            "body": "I guess it needs this change:\n```diff\ndiff --git a/src/nvim/winfloat.c b/src/nvim/winfloat.c\nindex 3b78a3c927..d92236603a 100644\n--- a/src/nvim/winfloat.c\n+++ b/src/nvim/winfloat.c\n@@ -122,6 +122,7 @@ win_T *win_new_float(win_T *wp, bool last, WinConfig fconfig, Error *err)\n void win_set_minimal_style(win_T *wp)\n {\n   wp->w_p_nu = false;\n+  wp->w_allbuf_opt.wo_nu = false;\n   wp->w_p_rnu = false;\n   wp->w_p_cul = false;\n   wp->w_p_cuc = false;\n```\nAnd similar changes for all other options set by `style = \"minimal\"`.\n\nOr it can use `set_option_direct_for()`.",
